<h1>All the people!!</h1>
<h2>Here are all the wonderful people you may or may not live with</h2>

<div>
    {{#if profiles}}
    {{#each profiles}}
        <div onClick="something goes in here.">
             <img src="/images/{{profiles.user_image}}" alt="{{profiles.name}}'s image'">
             <h2>{{profiles.name}}</h2>
        </div>
    {{/each}}
    {{else}}
    <p>
        *silence*... <br> 
        There doesn't seem to be anyone here. Perhaps you live alone? In that case, I am sorry to say that this is not the app for you.
    </p>
    {{/if}}
</div>